#  Functional Requirements — User Stories

## Admin User Stories

### US-1 — Admin Login
As an admin, I want to log in securely so that I can manage the system.

### US-2 — Manage Users
As an admin, I want to manage user accounts so that I can control system access.

### US-3 — Manage Rental Cars
As an admin, I want to add, update, or remove rental cars so that listings are accurate.

### US-4 — Manage Cars for Sale
As an admin, I want to manage cars for sale so that sold cars are not shown.

### US-5 — Manage Bookings
As an admin, I want to view and update bookings so that rentals are handled correctly.

### US-6 — Verify Payments
As an admin, I want to verify mobile banking payments so that bookings and purchases are confirmed.

### US-7 — Generate Reports
As an admin, I want to generate reports so that I can monitor system performance.
